## 2026-04-03 - Plugin sandbox message protocol audit — missing types and catch-all warning
- Fixed `TokenVariableBindingsMessage` in `types.ts`: type string was `'token-variable-bindings'` but sandbox (`variableSync.ts`) sends `'token-variable-bindings-result'`, and UI handler (`TokenUsages.tsx`) expects the same. Also corrected the field name from `bindings: { nodeId, nodeName, property }[]` to `variables: { name, collection, resolvedType }[]` to match what `scanTokenVariableBindings()` actually sends.
